to test this possibility, wild-type
mg63 cells were treated with protea-
some inhibitors,
including mg132
andlactacystinfollowedbyevaluation
of cellular differentiation. immuno-
blotanalysisrevealedthatadministra-
tion of these reagents at 10 ␮m clearly
