center research institute, tokyo) for critical reading of the manu-
script and drs. hidetaka yakura and kazuya mizuno (tokyo metro-
politan institute for neuroscience) for instructions on flow cytometry.
we are also indebted to hideki itabashi for help in preparing the
photographs.
